The band The Tap Tap, together with other performers, also recorded the so-called anthem against the world's downfall, entitled "World Fall Out".
Already today the anthem is very popular on YouTube. Will it also sound at the benefit concerts?
Of course, at the very end, provided that everything works and the world's downfall does not take place...
The anthem is to be sung simultaneously by all performers on all three concerts.
