After Madrid, Luxembourg, London and other cities where everything works better than with us, we were witnessing in Russia that everything in the East is still in its beginnings.
Moscow is absolutely not disabled-proof against Prague. There it is still unusual if someone is travelling in the wheelchair alone in the city centre.
